                            <li><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i>Multi Webpages</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-chess"></i>Built from Scratch</li>
                            <li><i class="fab fa-evernote"></i>Custom Integrations</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i>Custom Admin Panels</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-anchor"></i>Free Domain/Hosting</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-share-alt"></i>6-Month Maintenance</li> 
